body_html: A workaround is to replace the line from tensorflow.tools.compatibility import ast_edits with import ast_edits while making sure that the file ast_edits.py is in the same directory as the tf_upgrade.py script.
body_text: A workaround is to replace the line from tensorflow.tools.compatibility import ast_edits with import ast_edits while making sure that the file ast_edits.py is in the same directory as the tf_upgrade.py script.
body: A workaround is to replace the line `from tensorflow.tools.compatibility import ast_edits` with `import ast_edits` while making sure that the file [ast_edits.py](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/compatibility/ast_edits.py) is in the same directory as the `tf_upgrade.py` script.
